main_body:
The agricultural conversion rate applicable to the aid amounts shall be that in force  on the first day of the month in which the products are physically taken over by:
(a)  the industrial undertaking concerned in the case of the Azores and Madeira;
(b)  the first purchaser for the purposes of marketing fresh, the freezing undertaking or, where  applicable, the processing undertaking concerned in the case of the Canary Islands and Guiana.
